  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To elucidate whether blood lactate, lipid transfer proteins and PPARs/CLOCK/Bal1 have a
      circadian rhythm
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Blood will be drawn fasting and then every hour over a period of 24 hours in 30 healthy
      probands.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
